body:
English is fucking wild, kids

“You know that they’re supposed to be an odd couple, you know that I’m a bit fussy and a bit anal or whatever, and you’re a bit loose and a bit swaggery, and all that kind of stuff. But the specifics of that, you have to discover. And I remember in that table read, starting to discover those, and then they changed. I came in with sort of an idea and that idea went quite quickly. And you start to define yourself in terms of what the other person is doing.”

‘Brush up your English with Michael Sheen’, or that time when I read an interview about Good Omens and was starting to sweat nervously, because, come on, he didn’t confirm that, did he? And then, reluctantly went to look it up, and yup, there you go, there’s a second meaning. (From now on I’m going to drop the word in everyday conversation as often as possible, if only to measure from the level of shock in my counterpart’s facial expression how well educated they are.)

adjective

  • ‘Anal is defined as someone who is really uptight or particular and who always wants things a certain way.’
  • ‘An example of someone who is anal is a person who always lines up his socks by color and by level of wear, who perfectly folds them and puts them into specific boxes in his dresser and who insists on wearing them in a particular order.’

Aziraphale is anal

summary: To go with my last post: Is Michael going to get a BAFTA (or equivalent) for literally every facial expression and mannerism he...
body:
To go with my last post: Is Michael going to get a BAFTA (or equivalent) for literally every facial expression and mannerism he projected in Good Omens, or am I going to have to hand deliver one to him personally?

I’m not sure if he has much background in theatre or not, but I swear he is one of if not the most expressive actors I’ve ever seen (at least in this role) and he needs to be recognized for his talents.

summary:
My top 10 Crowley headcanons
He used to hangn out with Queen
He loves doing stuff to his hair. Usually he miracles it but...
body:
My top 10 Crowley headcanons

  1. He used to hangn out with Queen
  2. He loves doing stuff to his hair. Usually he miracles it but sometimes he likes to go to the barber
  3. He is not a coffe or a tea person. He likes cocoa
  4. His favorite colour is yellow even tho he would never admit it. Aziraphale once bought him a sunflower and he keeps it in a special room
  5. His favorite season is summer bc he loves the sun (your reptilian is showing Crowley)
  6. He is a secret animal activist. He trips anyone in the street wearing real leather or fur
  7. He knows the scientific name of every single plant, grass and tree
  8. He owns a small island in the caribbean. Sometimes he runs there to chill, especially in cold winter days. Aziraphale’s been there
  9. His loves strawberry daikiries and strawberry flavour things. Not the actual strawberries tho
  10. Even tho is cold and it rains a lot he loves London. He doesn’t really care for America.
  11. (Extra!) Crowley loves standing in silence in a corner in Aziraphale’s bookshop and see him walking around the shop, taking care of his books bc he hums to himself. Crowley thinks it’s adorable. Aziraphale does not know this
